  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to determine if a novel lead-based arm board is
      effective at reducing radiation dose to the operator during invasive cardiac procedures.
      Secondary objectives are to measure effect on radiation dose to patient and total fluoroscopy
      (x-ray) time.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
